  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Mix the flour, powdered sugar, evaporated milk, and melted butter together in a mixing bowl until smooth.",
    "Add Italian seasoning and salt to taste. Stir well.",
    "Fold in the chopped pistachios gently with a spatula.",
    "Transfer the mixture into an 8x8 inch baking dish.",
    "Bake for about 25-30 minutes or until golden brown on top.",
